  "CloudburstStarshine_name": "Cloudburst Starshine",
  "CloudburstStarshine_desc": "Amazingly, this savory Starshine can be drank by itself, or used as a sauce to compliment a main dish.",
  "BooBleGum_name": "Boo-Ble Gum",
  "BooBleGum_desc": "This seemingly innocent ball of plemon and jelbabu candy has been possessed! Well, not possessed. More like a ghost happened to pass through the crate of Boo-ble Gum. Blowing a bubble reveals a ghastly fanged face!",
  "DiggenBrownies_name": "Diggen Brownies",
  "DiggenBrownies_desc": "A chunk of fudge capped with dense creme-cheese. Topping it all off is a lovingly sculpted dark cocoa gravestone with a drizzling of gempas and lavapple blended preserves.",
  "CreepyCustard_name": "Creepy Custard",
  "CreepyCustard_desc": "This quivering flimflan and jelbabu based treat is practically trying to wiggle right out of its container! With its sweet, salacious, caramel glaze it's nowhere near creepy enough to avoid taking a spoon to it~",
  "SpookyCookie_name": "Spooky Cookie",
  "SpookyCookie_desc": "A crumbly speedwheel and flour based cookie with a crementin creme frosting. Spooky scary skeleton indeed!",
  "ScremeBars_name": "Screme Bars",
  "ScremeBars_desc": "A grownut and creme packed candybar contained by a thin layer of milk canmello-cocoa. So sensually sweet, it'll make you scream AND cream!",
  "ScarySnackums_name": "Scary Snackums",
  "ScarySnackums_desc": "A thick canmello-cocoa coated candybar. Stuffed with honey roasted grownut nougat and double chilled crementin. Scary? Not really. Scrumptious? Absolutely!",
  "Terremoto_name": "Terremoto",
  "Terremoto_desc": "Sweet wine, ice-cream, and a dash of sweet red juice. Alcoholic, refreshing, and energizing! A popular drink in the warmer regions of the world.",
  "StoutheartStarshine_name": "Stoutheart Starshine",
  "StoutheartStarshine_desc": "This sweet Starshine tastes almost like a fruity beverage! Drink too much though, and you are liable to forget the next day.",
  "StalwartStarshine_name": "Stalwart Starshine",
  "StalwartStarshine_desc": "The classic way to enjoy Starshine, uncomplicated, highly alcoholic, and enough for an entire party of one.",
  "RapidroidStarshine_name": "Rapidroid Starshine",
  "RapidroidStarshine_desc": "This particular Starshine will make your face twist up in masochistic delight thanks to its sour punch!",
  "MindseyeStarshine_name": "Mindseye Starshine",
  "MindseyeStarshine_desc": "This is a Starshine who's taste will linger on your tongue for hours, but not at the expense of its alcoholic content!",
  "Jackavapple_name": "Jackavapple",
  "Jackavapple_desc": "A sweet and Savory treat stuffed with mysterious soft sour chews, overflowing with spiced cream infused juice. Eat it, drink it, do it!",
  "HughMungus_name": "Hugh Mungus",
  "HughMungus_desc": "This teasingly taunting, meaty, monstrosity of a burger is guaranteed to satiate any monstrous appetite! Made with a scrubstick and bose blend patty, mando fries, a fried plankton egg and topped by two swirly cuts of eggtrap for zest.",
  "PeerlessStarshine_name": "Peerless Starshine",
  "PeerlessStarshine_desc": "This Starshine will taste like it's made from concentrated juice. It's not the flavor that will get you, it's the burn!",
  "Pavlova_name": "Pavlova",
  "Pavlova_desc": "Meringue clinging to a shell of light, crisp, pastry stuffed with sweet berries and topped with slices of green fruit. Named for a popular dancer from the central kingdom.",
  "NotPocket_name": "Not Pocket",
  "NotPocket_desc": "A spicy flour tortilla wrap fit to burst. Packed with zesty eggtrap, scrambled plankton eggs, bose, and diced shrubstick marinated in demon tail sauce! Don't worry, it's just a really spicy type of pepper.",
